[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Restart game year]]
Config parameter '''''restart_game_year''''' is located in the [NETWORK] section of the OPENTTD.cfg.  The value set to this parameter represents the year the server will restart. If the value is set to zero (0) the game will run until it is manually reset.  When set, the server will perform a restart on January 1st of value.

